==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scaturient
<hw>Sca*tu"ri*ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos><ety>[L.
<ets>scaturiens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>scaturire</ets> gush out, from
<ets>scatere</ets> to bubble, gush.]</ety> <def>Gushing forth; full to
overflowing; effusive.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A pen so <qex>scaturient</qex> and unretentive.</q> <rj><qau>Sir
W. Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scaturiginous</ent>⟦br⟧
